heading: Dark Ravine Dungeon Guide
content: Dark Ravine is a terrible dungeon that you should never as a Nightmare Dungeon. It's slow, takes forever to travel to and has a circular dungeon design. Also, it has Cultists and Demons - it's bad. Real bad. If you get Sigils for this one, grind them up into dust with . Tell the Occultist that Maxroll sent you. is useful enough though, so consider a first clear while you're leveling. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
